UWE Accommodation System

Desktop application capable of creating and storing information relevant to tenants, halls, and availability for a Hall manager to oversee.

UWE Chatbot

Improved students access to self-help material by using Python's SpaCy library, NLTK, and GPT 3.5 to create a chatbot which is capable of answering queries and providing links to necessary information.

EV Charging Point Locator

Using Bristol Open Data, this web application allows users to input their postcode to find the closest electric vehicle charging location via a map.
